properties.name: Auckland, New Zealand
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeaucklandIf I was going backpacking through New Zealand, Auckland is probably where I\'d start.

properties.name: Dubai, United Arab Emirates
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfedubaiI\'ve heard there is a seven star hotel here, I didn\'t know that was possible. Dubai is also home to the coolest man made islands anywhere.

properties.name: La Habana, Cuba
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeLa Habana, CubaOn my pro/con travel list vintage 50\'s cars and fine cigars far outweigh militant communism.

properties.name: London, England
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeLondon, UKAll anyone I\'ve ever met from London can do is talk about how much better it is than whatever American city they\'re in, I think they\'re bluffing but want to make sure.

properties.name: New York City, United States
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeNew York, NYIt\'s the biggest city in the country, 19 million+ people can\'t be wrong (except when cheering for the Yankees).

properties.name: Rome, Italy
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeRome, ItalyFor year I\'ve wanted to tear through Rome on a Vespa, maybe one day my dream can come true.

properties.name: San Jose, Costa Rica
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeSan Jose, Costa RicaTropical paradise if I don\'t get kidnapped.

properties.name: Seattle, United States
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeSeattleAfter playing way too much Microsoft Flight Simulator, I almost dropped out of college to get my private pilot\'s license to fly sea plane shuttles here. I\'m still in college but the dream\'s still there.

properties.name: Shanghai, China
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeshanghaiWhen I was in Beijing some friends of mine went to Shanghai and came back with awesome stories which solidified its place on this list.

properties.name: Sydney, Australia
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfeSydney, AustraliaI want to find out if they say "g\'day" that much and if Foster\'s really is Australian for beer.

properties.name: Tokyo, Japan
properties.description: Posted by AsheinfetokyoMy roommate\'s from Tokyo and he seems to like it.
